<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Lutz Tanner, Amtmann zu Neustadt an der Aisch, Konrad VI., Herr von Bickenbach und Burggraf von Miltenberg, und Hanneman Echter von Mespelbrunn, Viztum von Aschaffenburg</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Geleit für die Nürnberger Kaufleute auf dem Weg zu und von der Frankfurter Herbstmesse.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_499" id="249r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_499_r1l9">Lucʒen Tanner Amptman cʒu der <expan>Newe<ex>n</ex>ſtat</expan> An <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Ayſch </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_499_r1l10">Lıeber Lucʒ / VVir <expan>bit<ex>en</ex></expan> euch <expan>fleiſʒıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr vnſer <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_499_r1l11">vnd kauffleute vnd auch Jr habe vnd kauffmanſchaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_499_r1l12">vnd die Jren in die <expan>nehſtkünftige<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>frankfurt<ex>er</ex></expan> herbſtmeſſe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_499_r1l13">vnd vvıder darauſʒ mit geleyte <expan>fürſeh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet / Alſo <expan>vven<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_499_r1l14">ſie oder die Jren darümb cʒu ew oder den ~ ewren kumen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_499_r1l15">vnd des begern / daʒ ſie vnd daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan></del> <expan>alſu<ex>er</ex>re</expan> Jr <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_499_r1l16">von ewrs Ampts wegen cʒu der Newenſtat cʒu geleyten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_499_r1l17">habt ſıcher geleytet werden / Als etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_499_r1l18">vnd lat vns des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_499_r1l19"><expan>vviſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> bey diſem <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> diener <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab facs="#facs_499_r1l20"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu Pıckembach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_499_r1l21">vnd Burggraf cʒu <expan>Mılte<ex>m</ex>b<ex>er</ex>g</expan> <expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_499_r1l22"><expan>Han<ex>n</ex>man</expan> Echter <expan>vıcʒt<ex>um</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>Aſchaffemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> <expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_499" id="249r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Luczen Tanner, amptman czu der <expan>Newe<ex>n</ex>stat</expan> an
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Aysch </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber Lucz, wir <expan>bit<ex>en</ex></expan> euch
                                <expan>fleiszikl<ex>ich,</ex></expan> daz ir unser
                                <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> und kauffleute und auch ir habe und
                        kauffmanschaft und die iren in die <expan>nehstkünftige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Frankfurt<ex>er</ex></expan> herbstmesse und wider darausz mit
                        geleyte <expan>fürseh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet, also
                            <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> sie oder die iren darümb czu ew oder den
                        ewren kumen und des begern, daz sie und daz ir,
                            <expan>alsv<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> von
                        ewrs ampts wegen czu der Newenstat czu geleyten habt, sicher geleytet
                        werden, als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und lat uns des
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>freuntl<ex>ich,</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> bey
                        disem <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> diener. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
                        ut <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad,</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re<ex>n</ex></expan> czu Pickembach und burggraf czu
                                <expan>Milte<ex>m</ex>b<ex>er</ex>g,</expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan><lb/> H<expan>an<ex>n</ex>man</expan>
                        Echter, <expan>viczt<ex>um</ex></expan> czu
                            <expan>Aschaffemb<ex>ur</ex>g,</expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
